data.description: Welcome to 225 Sylvia Road! This ranch-style home, nestled in the heart of Belton, provides a great opportunity for empty nesters, small families, and first-time homebuyers alike. Situated in a quiet and well-maintained neighborhood with NO HOA, you'll love the privacy offered by the 0.75-acre lot, which backs up to a scenic tree line. Inside the home, you'll enjoy the cozy, open-concept living space with vaulted ceilings and plenty of room to relax with family or friends. Off of the living room, a separate office space is perfect for those who work from home or need an extra space for crafting, homeschooling, or storage. The split-floor plan allows for ample privacy in the master suite and the spare bedrooms.Functionality in this home is a breeze with great storage space in the kitchen, closets, and the two-car garage. Not to mention, an updated roof and HVAC system allow for peace of mind for the new owners. The property's location adds to its appeal, providing easy access to essential amenities, schools, and other conveniences. All that's missing is your personal touch. Make this beautiful and functional home yours - schedule your showing today! PROPERTY QUALIFIES FOR 100% USDA FINANCING!
